        <abstract> 
<p>Comments on his own review of Bates’s butterfly paper [<hi rend="italic">Collected papers</hi> 2: 87–92].</p>  
<p>Thanks AG for information on <hi rend="italic">Platanthera</hi>.</p>  
<p>Has been wasting more time with Melastomataceae; can find no nectar in <hi rend="italic">Monochaetum</hi>; is there any in <hi rend="italic">Rhexia</hi>?</p> 
            <p>Hopes Lincoln’s "fiat against Slavery" will have some effect.</p>
        </abstract>
